# ============================================================
# Deepotus Video Gen — Environment Variables Template
# ============================================================
# Copy this file to `backend/.env` and fill in YOUR keys.
# NEVER commit your real `.env` to git or share it in chat.
#
# Rules for editing:
#   - No spaces around `=`     → FAL_KEY=fal-... (NOT FAL_KEY = fal-...)
#   - No quotes around values  → FAL_KEY=fal-... (NOT FAL_KEY="fal-...")
#   - No trailing whitespace
#   - Save as UTF-8 (NOT UTF-16 — Notepad sometimes does this; use VS Code if unsure)
#
# After editing, you MUST restart the backend (Ctrl+C the backend PowerShell window,
# then re-run scripts/run.ps1). Pydantic-settings does not hot-reload .env.
# ============================================================


# --- fal.ai (Seedance 2.0 image-to-video) -- REQUIRED ---
#
# Get your key:    https://fal.ai/dashboard/keys
# Format:          fal-... (long alphanumeric)
# Cost:            ~$0.30 per 5s 1080p Seedance Pro clip
#                  ~$0.40 per 5s 1080p Seedance Lite first-last-frame clip
# Free tier:       fal.ai offers some free credits to new accounts
# Without this:    Seedance and Composition providers won't work (HeyGen-only still possible)
#
FAL_KEY=


# --- HeyGen (avatar videos + composition) -- REQUIRED for HeyGen/Composition features ---
#
# Get your key:    https://app.heygen.com/api (Settings → API → New Key)
# Format:          sk_V2_hgu_... OR hg_... (depends on your account tier)
# Cost:            Pay-as-you-go in credits, no free tier
#                  Avatar V: ~6 credits per minute of generated video
#                  Photo Avatar creation: ~0.2 credits
#                  Avatar IV (premium): ~10 credits per minute
# Top up at:       https://app.heygen.com/billing (minimum $5)
# Without this:    HeyGen and Composition tabs will be disabled in the UI
#
# CRITICAL: The key is shown ONCE at creation time. Copy it immediately or you'll
# need to regenerate. If you regenerate, the old key is revoked.
#
HEYGEN_API_KEY=


# --- ElevenLabs (voiceover FR/EN) -- OPTIONAL ---
#
# Get your key:    https://elevenlabs.io/app/settings/api-keys
# Format:          long alphanumeric string
# Cost:            Free tier: 10,000 chars/month; Starter: $5/mo for 30,000 chars
# Without this:    Voiceover features are silently disabled. Seedance/HeyGen still work.
#
# Note: HeyGen has its own built-in TTS, so ElevenLabs is only useful for:
#   - Voiceover on Seedance clips (no avatar)
#   - Higher quality narration than HeyGen for non-avatar content
#
ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=


# --- ElevenLabs Voice IDs (optional, defaults work for most use cases) ---
#
# These are the default voices used per language. Change only if you have a
# preferred voice cloned in your ElevenLabs account.
#
# Default EN:  Rachel (clear professional female voice)
# Default FR:  Dorothy (warm narrator voice)
#
# Browse voices at: https://elevenlabs.io/app/voice-library
#
ELEVENLABS_VOICE_ID_EN=21m00Tcm4TlvDq8ikWAM
ELEVENLABS_VOICE_ID_FR=ThT5KcBeYPX3keUQqHPh


# --- Paths (auto-configured by setup-paths.ps1, override only if needed) ---
#
# These are usually picked up automatically. Override only if you have a non-standard
# install of Python or ffmpeg.
#
# PYTHON_EXE_PATH=
# FFMPEG_BIN_PATH=


# --- News scraper (v1.7) ---
#
# The scraper defeats cookie/consent banners + UA blocks (browser headers,
# pre-accepted consent cookies, AMP). For Google-News-wrapped links and
# hard-blocked sites it also uses a public reader proxy (r.jina.ai) to
# recover the article body. ON by default; when it triggers, the target
# URL is sent to that third party. Set to false to never contact it.
#
ARTICLE_READER_FALLBACK=true


# --- Telegram auto-publish (v1.9 Scheduler) -- OPTIONAL ---
#
# The reference auto-publish channel: free, no app review, supports video.
# 1. Create a bot: talk to @BotFather on Telegram -> /newbot -> copy the token
# 2. Add the bot as ADMIN of your channel/group
# 3. Get the chat id: forward a channel message to @userinfobot, or use
#    https://api.telegram.org/bot<TOKEN>/getUpdates after posting once
# Without these: scheduled posts flip to "ready" instead of auto-posting,
# and you publish manually with one click (assisted mode).
#
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=


# --- Ollama local LLM (marketing plans, v1.11) -- OPTIONAL ---
#
# Run your plans on a LOCAL model: free, and your strategy never leaves
# your machine. Install Ollama (ollama.com), pull a model, set it here:
#   ollama pull qwen2.5:14b-instruct
# Recommended: qwen2.5:14b-instruct or better. 8B models are the floor —
# below that, plan quality drops sharply. When both Anthropic and Ollama
# are configured, Anthropic wins (better quality); Ollama is the fallback.
#
OLLAMA_URL=http://127.0.0.1:11434
OLLAMA_MODEL=


# --- Anthropic (news article summaries + marketing plan generator) -- OPTIONAL ---
#
# When set, selected news articles get a faithful, neutral 2-3 sentence
# summary (Claude Haiku) BEFORE the deepotus 'prophet' cynical/humorous
# tone is applied. Without it, the pipeline stays deterministic (extracted
# essence / RSS snippet).
# Get a key: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys  (format sk-ant-...)
# Cost: a few $0.001 per article (Haiku). Leave empty to disable.
#
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-haiku-4-5-20251001


# ============================================================
# Verification (after filling and restarting backend)
# ============================================================
#
# curl http://localhost:8765/api/health
#
# Expected: {"ok":true, "version":"1.8.0",
#            "fal_configured":true,       <- True if FAL_KEY filled
#            "heygen_enabled":true,       <- True if HEYGEN_API_KEY filled
#            "voiceover_enabled":true,    <- True if ELEVENLABS_API_KEY filled
#            ...}
#
# If any value is false but you filled the key, check:
#   1. No quotes around the value
#   2. No leading/trailing spaces
#   3. Saved the file (Notepad asks before closing — say yes)
#   4. Restarted the backend (the dev server doesn't reload .env)
# ============================================================
